OL,3,CBorders MP, John Lamont, named as new
OL,4,CShadow Scottish Secretary
OL,6,FJohn Lamont, the Member of Parliament
OL,7,Ffor Berwickshire, Roxburgh and Selkirk
OL,8,Fhas been named Shadow Secretary of
OL,9,FState for Scotland.
OL,11,FMr Lamont was one of five Conservative
OL,12,FMPs to be elected north of the border.
OL,14,FHe has previously served as a minister
OL,15,Fin the Scotland Office under the
OL,16,FConservative government.
