OL,3,CBorders MP, John Lamont, named as new
OL,4,CShadow Scottish Secretary
OL,6,FMr Lamont said: "It's important that
OL,7,Fwe ensure the new United Kingdom
OL,8,Fgovernment delivers on the huge
OL,9,Finvestment that the previous
OL,10,FConservative government was delivering
OL,11,Fin Scotland, we can't see any
OL,12,Fretreating from that record level of
OL,13,Finvestment, and they need to continue
OL,14,Fto work constructively with the
OL,15,FScottish Government."
OL,17,FAlister Jack who previously filled the
OL,18,Frole, did not stand in this election
OL,19,Fand was awarded a knighthood for his
OL,20,Fservices.
