OL,3,CBorders MP, John Lamont, named as new
OL,4,CShadow Scottish Secretary
OL,6,FThe Edinburgh MP Ian Murray is the new
OL,7,FScottish Secretary in the Labour
OL,8,Fgovernment and said they were elected
OL,9,Fto deliver change.
OL,11,FHe said: "Change is about resetting
OL,12,Fthe relationships we've had across the
OL,13,Fcountry, particularly in this context
OL,14,Fwith the Scottish government.
OL,16,F"The Prime Minister and First Minister
OL,17,Fhad a very, very productive meeting on
OL,18,FSunday which I attended with the
OL,19,FDeputy First Minister, about resetting
OL,20,Fthat relationship.
